<div class="black"><div class="container" role="main">
    <div class="row" id="who">
      <h1 class="text-center">Who is HUG?</h1>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-8">
          <p class="lead">We're just people who show up and make music!</p>
          <p>Anyone is welcome to drop by and join in.  If you don't have an ukulele, we're happy to have other accompaniment.  We can always use more voices to join in and sing!</p>
          <p>Feel free to join our <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/332494077495/">Facebook Group</a> to stay up-to-date with the next events and more.</p>

      </div>
