      <h1 class="text-center">Where do HUG meet?</h1>
      <div class="col-md-6">
            <p class="lead">We play at <a href="http://www.stonemasons-arms.co.uk/find-us">The Stonemasons Arms</a>, in Hammersmith, London. </p>
