        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p class="lead">We are currently meeting on the <strong>second and fourth Monday</strong> of each month.  </p>
            <p>Check our calendar for the next HUG Jam date.</p>
            <p>The function room opens at 7:30pm, and we tend to play until closing.  Drop in any time, but we tend to play the easier songs toward the start of the evening.</p>
